Seven men have been shot and killed, execution-style, outside Durban. Courtesy #DStv403 ADAMS, Durban - KZN police have launched a manhunt following the killing of seven people in eMsahweni, near Adams, on the outskirts of Durban. Police say they were shot execution-style around 6pm on Wednesday. READ: Police investigating KZN mass murder The victims were between the ages of 21 and 36 and in a house when they were attacked.